{"kind":"article","metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapsNativeSDK"}],"roleHeading":"Article","title":"Переход с JS MapsSDK","role":"article"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/mapsnativesdk\/updatesdk"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK"]]},"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/UpdateSdk","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"text":"Сделайте переход со старого JS MapsSDK на MapsNativeSDK максимально просто.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"MapsNativeSDK позволяет получить вам совершенно новый опыт работы с картографической информацией в ваших приложениях в сравнении с ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/maps-mailru\/maps-sdk-ios","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":". В этом руководстве будет описан процесс перехода с прошлой версии на новую.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"%D0%A3%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%BA%D0%B0-MapsNativeSDK","text":"Установка MapsNativeSDK","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"MapsNativeSDK является не обновлением для JS MapsSDK, а полноценной новой библиотекой, поэтому вы не сможете совершить переход с помощью обновления пакета в SPM, пода в CocoaPods. Вам необходимо произвести установку MapsNativeSDK одним из способов, описанных в статье ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/StartUsing"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","text":"Переход на MapsNativeSDK","level":2,"anchor":"%D0%9F%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B5%D1%85%D0%BE%D0%B4-%D0%BD%D0%B0-MapsNativeSDK"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Для осуществления перехода на новую версию SDK сделайте следующий шаги:"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Шаг 1. Конфигурирование SDK","level":3,"anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-1-%D0%9A%D0%BE%D0%BD%D1%84%D0%B8%D0%B3%D1%83%D1%80%D0%B8%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-SDK"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"MapsNativeSDK требует произвести конфигурирование SDK до создания первого экземпляра "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MapView"},{"text":". Для конфигурирования служит метод ","type":"text"},{"code":"MapsSDKConfigurator\/setup(baseURL:apiKey:diskCachePath:maxCacheSizeBytes:fileTimeoutSec:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". Подробнее о его использовании можно прочитать в статье ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/StartUsing"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","\/\/ Предварительное конфигурирование SDK не требовалось","","\/\/ СТАЛО","MapsSDKConfigurator.setup(apiKey: ##API-ключ##)"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Шаг 2. Конфигурирование MapView","level":3,"anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-2-%D0%9A%D0%BE%D0%BD%D1%84%D0%B8%D0%B3%D1%83%D1%80%D0%B8%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-MapView"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Теперь конфигурацию карты (стартовое положение камеры, стартовый стиль), а так же делегат необходимо передавать в инициализатор объекта "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MapView"},{"type":"text","text":" ("},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapView\/init(frame:configuration:delegate:)"},{"type":"text","text":")."}]},{"code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","\/\/ Создаем объект карты","let mapView = MapView()","\/\/ Создаем объект конфигурации","let mapConfig = MapViewConfig(","    apiKey: \"##API_KEY##\",","    center: Coordinates(lng: 33, lat: 55),","    zoomLevel: 11,","    style: .automatic",")","\/\/ Устанавливаем конфигурацию","mapView.setup(mapConfig)","\/\/ Устанавливаем делегат","mapView.delegate = self","","\/\/ СТАЛО","let configuration = MapConfiguration(","    center: Coordinates(","        lng: 35.910974,","        lat: 56.859207","    ),","    zoom: 15,","    predefinedStyle: style,","    selectFeatures: .all,","    cameraMode: .earth",")","\/\/ Передаем конфигурацию и позже отдельно устанавливаем делегат","mapView = MapView(configuration: configuration)","mapView.delegate = self","","\/\/ ИЛИ","\/\/ Передаем конфигурацию и делегат одновременно","mapView = MapView(configuration: configuration, delegate: self)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"text":"Шаг 3. Изменение методов перемещение камеры","anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-3-%D0%98%D0%B7%D0%BC%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%82%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%BE%D0%B2-%D0%BF%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%89%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%BA%D0%B0%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%80%D1%8B","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Для перемещения камеры теперь необходимо обращаться к контроллеру "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/CameraController","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" через свойство "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapView\/camera","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". Ранее методы управления находились непосредственно в API класса "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MapView"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Для перемещения камеры используется методы группы "},{"code":"flyTo","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" и другие. Подробнее об это читайте в статье ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/CameraMoving","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","mapView.flyTo(Coordinates(lng: 33, lat: 55), animated: true, duration: 2)","","\/\/ СТАЛО","mapView.camera.flyTo(coordinates: .center(Coordinates(lng: 37.427278, lat: 55.756486)), ","                        cameraOptions: .init(bearing: 80, zoom: 12, pitch: 0), ","                        animationOptions: .init(easing: .easeInOut, duration: .max(value: 2)))"],"type":"codeListing"},{"level":3,"anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-4-%D0%98%D0%B7%D0%BC%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%82%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%BE%D0%B2-%D1%83%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B2%D0%BB%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D1%8F-%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B4%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%82%D0%BE%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%BC-%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%8C%D0%B7%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0%D1%82%D0%B5%D0%BB%D1%8F","text":"Шаг 4. Изменение методов управления индикатором пользователя","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Для управления индикатором пользователя на карте необходимо обращаться к контроллеру ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/UserPointerController"},{"text":" через свойство ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapView\/userPointer"},{"text":". Ранее методы управления находились непосредственно в API класса ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MapView"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Для отображения и перемещения индикатора пользователя используется группа методов ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setCurrentLocation"},{"text":". Подробнее об это читайте в статье ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/UserPointer","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","mapView.setCurrentLocation(Coordinates(lng: 33, lat: 55), bearing: 0, accuracy: 0)","","\/\/ СТАЛО","mapView.userPointer.setCurrentLocation(","    coordinates: Coordinates(lng: 33, lat: 55),","    bearing: 0,","    accuracy: 0,","    animationDuration: 1)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"level":3,"anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-5-%D0%98%D0%B7%D0%BC%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%BB%D0%BE%D0%B3%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%B8-%D0%BE%D0%B1%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B1%D0%BE%D1%82%D0%BA%D0%B8-%D1%81%D0%BE%D0%B1%D1%8B%D1%82%D0%B8%D0%B9-%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%80%D1%82%D1%8B","text":"Шаг 5. Изменение логики обработки событий карты","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"В MapsNativeSDK сильно переработана система событий, они стали более логичными. Теперь практически для всех типов событий (перемещение камеры, клики по маркерам, события жизненного цикла карты) используется метод ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapViewDelegate\/mapView(_:didReceiveEvent:)-7k969","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Более подробно об обработке событий читайте в статье "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/Lifecycle","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Пример отслеживания событий нажатия на маркер"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapView(_ map: MapView, didSelectMarkerID markerID: String) {}","    func mapView(_ map: MapView, didReceiveEvent event: String) {","            \/\/ ...","            \/\/ event.type = .clickOnMarker","            \/\/ ...","        }","}","","\/\/ СТАЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapView(_ map: MapView, didReceiveEvent event: MapEvent) {","        switch event {","            \/\/ ...","            \/\/ event.type = .platformMarkerDidSelect","            \/\/ или","            \/\/ event.type = .markerDidSelect","            \/\/ ...","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"В данный момент MapsNativeSDK имеет две реализации функционала маркеров: ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PlatformMarker"},{"text":" и ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/Marker"},{"text":". В дальнейшем этот API будет отмечен, как устаревший, его заменит единая более совершенная реализация маркеров.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Warning","style":"warning","type":"aside"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Пример отслеживания событий перемещения камеры"}]}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapView(_: MapView, didMoveCenterToCoords coords: Coordinates, zoom: Double, bounds: MapBounds) {}","    func mapView(_: MapView, didChangeZoom zoom: Double, scale: Double) {}","}","","\/\/ СТАЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapView(_ map: MapView, didReceiveEvent event: MapEvent) {","        switch event {","            \/\/ ...","            \/\/ event.type = .cameraDidMove","            \/\/ ...","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Пример отслеживания событий загрузки карты"}],"type":"strong"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapViewDidLoad(_: MapView) {","        \/\/ ...","    }","}","","\/\/ СТАЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapView(_ map: MapView, didReceiveEvent event: MapEvent) {","        switch event {","            \/\/ ...","            \/\/ event.type = .mapDidShow","            \/\/ ...","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Пример отслеживания событий тапа по карте"}],"type":"strong"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","class MapDelegate: MapV